<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When instantiating an instance of Zend_File_Transfer, the following exception is thrown:</p>

<p>Zend_File_Transfer_Exception: Adapter Zend_File_Transfer_Adapter_Http does not extend Zend_File_Transfer_Adapter' in /path/to/Zend/File/Transfer.php on line 56</p>

<p>As of ZF 1.9.6, there is no Zend_File_Transfer_Adapter. Instead, the adapters need to extend Zend_File_Transfer_Adapter_Abstract. The attached patch fixes the condition and exception message to reflect this.</p>

    </div>
